Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天在后山好像发生了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 好像出现了别国的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警卫部队打倒了其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且回收了尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今天别让学生们靠近后山比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许还留有残党呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿平安无事才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体呢 尸体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然经常在这附近晃悠比较熟悉 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该问一下他们详细的地点来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干吗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上回学校去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里依旧有危险分子存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受人所托 怎么能半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是你的指导老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥只有这种时候才摆出一副老师的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师根本不理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我回学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是被同伴疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不关心我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这次不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我将战利品带回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就会认同我这个伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就不再是孤单一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想体会那种感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我一定要将战利品带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不能让你留在这座危险的后山里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 我的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀 色诱术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人还真是单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…战斗过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 在这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真头痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天什么都没吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么可吃的东西呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种形状我从没见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是昨天战斗时 敌方忍者用的苦无了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来 我找到战利品了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把苦无
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们要寻找的密函吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在被打倒之前 他把苦无藏在了鸟窝里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大功告成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是个麻烦的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便应付一下他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子…就这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对他一点也不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母双亡后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也没有人夸奖我 认可我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在班上 我经常干蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我希望被人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟当时的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以借我点钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 你把零花钱全花在零食上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了零食 我还能花在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借你一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还在上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跟陌生人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则老爸会跟我发火的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈良鹿丸和秋道丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道我们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是鹿角和丁座的儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得真像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把你们翘课的事告诉他们好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天改自习课了 是吧 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人去后山找尸体了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡老师随后就去找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡老师去找鸣人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 自习不代表下课了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快回学校去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我也有同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖将那把苦无交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这个我绝对不会给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 看来我们得动粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色诱术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾 这个术可不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直就是犯规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 分身术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次见到这么不中用的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍术如果不管用的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对这座森林里布置的陷阱可是了如指掌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 怎么能被这种不入流的陷阱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小兔崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个陷阱在哪儿来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清醒点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了 一起回学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些外人在木叶鬼鬼祟祟地想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老老实实地把那个小鬼交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾这个傻瓜学生很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此你也要小命不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越傻越可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且我也不是那么容易被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 包围他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会保护好鸣人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑 散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影多重手里剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你的学生那听到了一些消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增援来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起收拾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁连携术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走 伊鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迦楼罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是卡卡西先生及时赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅凭我一人 怕是难以脱险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有你一个 也能保护好鸣人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我似乎有些明白卡卡西先生的那番话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未直面过鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是在不断地回避着他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今后我一定会直面鸣人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…木叶村的警卫部署
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是她们潜入的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽快调整村里的警备部署
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说事出偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这次鸣人的莽撞反而拯救了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您让我成为了鸣人的指导老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因此我才会想起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经我决定做一名老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:14:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为您那时对我的一番教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经一年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将悲伤压抑在笑容之下 很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你指导老师那儿听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在学校里总是大家开心的焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…才没有悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者死于任务是一种荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲也好 母亲也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是用性命从妖狐手中保卫了村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我则是英雄之子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会孤单 不会难过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是喜悦之泪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你总是孤单一人抱膝而坐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶村的忍者们都拥有火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想要保卫这个村子的强烈愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是拥有这个意志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的大伙们都是他的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡 你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想将第三代的火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传给后人 传给鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 为啥将我辛苦找回的战利品给弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 你差点丢了小命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎么这么听话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让我第一次看到伊鲁卡老师发这么大火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师决定以后要好好关注你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 从明天起会严格调教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈发不想去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你拥有火之意志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志 那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想要保护这个村子的强烈愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你拥有它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能变得如火影大人般的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影真的那么厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不只是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影大人还深受村民们的敬仰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是引领我们的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是从妖狐手中保护了村子的英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为比第四代更厉害的火影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后用我的力量得到大家的认同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你长这么高的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就能当上火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会拼命努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要成功给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没准真能成为火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡老师 过来帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我这就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水月去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两三天前出去后就没回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好别回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都听到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩首大刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还惦记着它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就怪你当时没带上它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我找得好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和八尾那种怪物交战时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁还有空管这种累赘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把半死不活的你们扛回来的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别内讧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真以恩人自居了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他呢 反正也找回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了它果然缺乏斗志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下人都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤势痊愈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面前往木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到佩因会战败
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大跌眼镜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小南也不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 一下子少了这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要一个能和外道魔像同步的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼鲛 你去找八尾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有其他事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会这么惨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是佩因所为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过鸣人已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打倒了佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人他…那九尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他凭借自己的力量压制了九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人自己将九尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可没工夫让你吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来重建村子可不轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我们需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召开紧急会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上忍班长鹿角先生 请立刻前往大名殿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是鸣人的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个傻小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你来负责教导最为合适
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外宇智波佐助也在你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会那么简单就心慈手软的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.71,0:22:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指导上忍 旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来相当棘手啊
